@5566 = ~DEATHBRINGER: Deathbringers are a special group of warriors of Bhaal trained in the art of intimidation and war. Those trained in the ways of the Deathbringer may fell their foes with a single blow, and every enemy slain at their hand fuels their rage and ferocity.. They are also a group of scattered cultists that are still trying to revive Bhaal, even though his essence is locked up in the Upper Planes.

